{"tid":857120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇連登就黎變高登","createTime":"2018-10-11T02:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T02:55:06.000Z","uid":56546,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"778b29672ac470f810e008709e5178587966e342","tid":857120,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T02:32:39.000Z","msg":"如果admin再唔block 7班五毛走狗<br />\n<br />\n好快呢度會同以前高登一鳩樣<br />\n每一頁每個post都係五毛洗版<br />\n<br />\n跟住一班正常會員當然睇唔過眼<br />\n大家就喺度不斷追擊對方<br />\n嚴重影響成個論壇討論氣氛<br />\n<br />\n成版post根本係同一班人開, 係度互屌<br />\n成個討論區嘅話題極度單一化<br />\n當年呢個亦係高登死因之一<br />\n<br />\n所以唔該admin唔好再持住咩自由討論原則乜春都唔做"},{"pid":"0da929a3c70fde0c0cee1891a988355e2e2e5ee7","tid":857120,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T02:33:49.000Z","msg":"Admin本身就企支那果邊"},{"pid":"2852b2cd8fc87ed068828069a93d3508e9460216","tid":857120,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T02:35:13.000Z","msg":"哩度admin奶得仲犀利過阿早,咪咁弱智啦"},{"pid":"32b4194441501ce38c659f191ac5b47bf3c40e40","tid":857120,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T02:36:01.000Z","msg":"笑到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a6a90cc47c030875f4d4803544cbec0a33c6e0","tid":857120,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2852b2cd8fc87ed068828069a93d3508e9460216","tid":857120,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T02:35:13.000Z","msg":"哩度admin奶得仲犀利過阿早,咪咁弱智啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T02:38:07.000Z","msg":"咁要睇admin係咪同錢作對執意奶共<br />\n<br />\n今日連登搶到高登班會員<br />\n他朝一樣可以有另一個論壇彈起搶走連登會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9861937c6d36c8415d19ca7d42385094e2137bf6","tid":857120,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32b4194441501ce38c659f191ac5b47b